  }), mdx("p", null, "So we got this new DSLR, a Nikon D7000 and a 50mm AF f1.8D standard lens. I\u2019ve been dying to have this opportunity to be able to take decent photos and this is a heaven-sent chance for me to say goodbye to poor mediocre photography. For all these years I\u2019ve suffered enough taking horrible photos using point-and-shoot digital cameras and reminiscing good ole memories in grainy camera phone shots."), mdx("p", null, "I am now starting to learn how to shoot properly."), mdx("p", null, "Since photography is one of the most common hobbies since the boom of digital cameras, most are tempted to label themselves ", mdx("strong", {
